{"tid":404250,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"全盛時期卡域克 謝四 林八 你會點排？","createTime":"2017-09-18T02:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T12:00:30.000Z","uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd3baeda7a813a3193171a630ac30fc0d8db5c0","tid":404250,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"1.卡域克：中場控制節奏勁，重要時候現位幫手，企位靚收窄對方進攻空間同埋截波，傳波力水掌握有道易拎又穿到人，仲有埋準繩遠射，技巧識睇位射岩岩好收死龍門，全盛果期可以同小白相比。<br />\n<br />\n2.謝四：遠射真係勁，可同卡域克相比。比奧雲既長傳特別毒辣，3:2贏阿根廷果場功架非常，但整體都係輸比卡叔。贏既有體能勁，通場飛，四圍駁腳同做防守。<br />\n<br />\n3.林伯：遠射都幾勁，但輸卡域克半班，國家隊表現唔知雙特效應定點，硬係無車仔咁勁，所以應該拎走佢擺卡域克搭謝四。防守力欠奉，但極度穩陣，好少斷波。"},{"pid":"56662e075bd9116b29c665e1e1abbb4babba58bf","tid":404250,"uid":50385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"[認真認論]其實卡域克勁係邊點解成日吹奏？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/398689/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/398689/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n而家又話可以同小白相比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeefa806f43ef01ec745d2d9e127d5d142175b9f","tid":404250,"uid":102240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[認真認論]其實卡域克勁係邊點解成日吹奏？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/398689/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/398689/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n而家又話可以同小白相比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSickball了"},{"pid":"6eac3ed72ecab73d5f969b921182c001950b1083","tid":404250,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"我 我 我"},{"pid":"d89131899add731ac31ce426cf9c77285c5206bf","tid":404250,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:19:17.000Z","msg":"林伯廢過謝4?<br />\n04 Euro 就林伯 carry，謝拉特有邊次大賽有貨交？"},{"pid":"c8a9b3e302696a5f10ce2ef3e90c489